# trap: trapezoidal spin-lock waveform
# parameters should be adjusted according to experiment
# H.Desvaux, P.Berthault, N.Birlirakis, M.Goldman, M.Piotto,
# JMR 113A (1995) 47 
%
#       Shape Parameters
#       ----------------
amf 	= tra	 (amplitude modulation function)
fla 	= 54.7t	 (default tilt angle)
pwbw 	= 1.0	 (dummy pulsewidth to bandwidth product)
stretch = 5.0    (stretching factor)
dash    = stretch (dash parameter)
steps 	= 1000	 (default number of steps)

